summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3652, for the improvement of the alley Block 23 and 24, 2nd Supplemental Crown Addition, being the alley between 10th Avenue West and 11th Avenue West, from West Garfield Street to West Galer Street, by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 45063 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
